  "body": "# ðŸ’Ž Issue\r\n\r\n### Background\r\nBLST defines two function aggregating public keys: [`AggregatePublicKeys`](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/shared/bls/blst/public_key.go#L56) and [`Aggregate`](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/shared/bls/blst/public_key.go#L94).\r\n\r\nThe former validates public keys properly, but the latter doesn't.\r\n[https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature-04#section-5.1](https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature-04#section-5.1) requires first validating public keys.\r\n\r\ncc: @veorq",
